  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your super cute character and put him in-front of a barrage of bombs, spikes and whatever else can kill you. <br><br>Dodge this is an awesome and crazy game where you need to stay alive as long as possible.<br>The game gets more difficult the longer you live and only the best reflexes will reach the top.<br><br>The game is played with the mouse and has a great physics engine to keep everything feeling like you are really getting pounded and blown up!</h2>",
